---
title: Sticky Mango Paneer Noodles with Stir-Fried Veg
description: Looking for a quick and tasty midweek dinner option? Try cooking up our Sticky Mango Paneer Noodles in just 20-25 minutes for a delicious and speedy meal.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/HF_Y24_R17_W26_UK_V22127-3_Main_low-23e9ed5f.jpg
